  <description><![CDATA[<p>The owners, Françoise &amp; Olivier Deffaugt look forward to welcoming our guests to their family-run property. The cuisine at the Neige et Roc is fabulous and has received recognition as a ‘Maitre Restauranteur’ for their use of fresh produce. Relax around the fireplace in the lounge with a drink from the bar or head to the pool for a swim and book a massage locally for ultimate indulgence. The resort centre and shops are a short walk away.</p>]]></description>
