  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have WC, bath with shower head attachment or shower room, cable / satellite flat screen TV with English speaking channels, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, mini bar, telephone, towels, toiletries, bath robes, slippers, hairdryer, safe and a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<ul>
<li>Standard double room (A2): sleeps up to 2 people (18m²) in a double bed. Also available for sole occupancy</li>
<li>Superior twin room (B2): sleeps up to 2 people (22m²) in double/twin beds</li>
<li>Triple room (C3): sleeps up to 3 people (22m²) in a double bed and additional single bed suitable for child up to 12 years</li>
<li>Junior suite (D4): sleeps up to 4 people (33m²) in a double bedroom and twin bedroom, separated by a door</li>
<li>Deluxe suite (E4): sleeps up to 3 people (45m²) in double/twin beds with a sofa bed in the lounge area</li>
</ul>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available on request. A2 rooms do not include tea &amp; coffee facilities or mini bar.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
